datatable.name: framework_admin_datatable
datatable.sql: CREATE TABLE `framework_admin ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `mobile` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `password` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `photo` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `question` text NOT NULL, `answer` text NOT NULL, `code` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(), `level` int(11) NOT NULL, `status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, `permission` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1

datatable.name: framework_project_datatable
